				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[If there is no information available from the protein isolation kit provider, or if the laboratories own validated protein isolation procedures are used, the isolated proteins should be assessed immediately. Where the protein cannot be assayed immediately, the laboratory shall have verified procedures in place how to store the isolated protein.]]></text>
